data.description: Discover your dream country living retreat with extensive RV parking! This home boasts an open concept floor plan flooded with natural light. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight with brand new appliances including refrigerator! Enjoy the tranquility of no backyard neighbors on a quiet ending street with no HOA! The main level features new Anderson windows and flooring throughout. Security System through Vivant! Solar panels so say goodbye to high electricity costs and hello to low cost energy bills Minutes from multiple local wineries, schools, and scenic hiking trails, this property offers the perfect blend of relaxation and convenience. You're only 20 minutes from shopping, entertainment, and medical facilities. Plus, with RV parking expanded for extra toys, you'll have ample space for all your outdoor adventures. Immerse yourself in nature with Succor Creek just 100 yards away and the Snake River only half a mile, providing year-round recreational opportunities. Best country living experience!
